Package: soundlocalization
Title: Isolate and Localize Sound from Simultaneous Recordings
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Luciano", "Moffatt", , "lmoffatt@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4994-4304"))
Description: This package allow to load, align, separate in portions and isolate and localize in space sounds from the environment with emphasis in birds and frogs. 
